---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Teachers | 7-Day Phật Thất Retreat at Bodh Gaya">
    <section class="max-w-4xl py-16 space-y-10">
        <div>
            <p class="mb-3 text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-neutral-500">Teachers</p>
            <h1 class="mb-6">Retreat Leadership</h1>
            <p class="max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-neutral-700">
                The retreat is guided by monastics from Viên Giác Patriarchal Monastery and its affiliated monasteries in Europe, accompanying participants
                throughout the days of practice in Bodh Gaya.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-6">
            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-6">
                <h2 class="mb-2">Thầy Hạnh Tấn</h2>
                <p class="mb-4 text-neutral-500">Amitayus Monastery, Dippoldiswalde – Germany</p>
                <p class="leading-8 text-neutral-700">
                    Guiding the retreat and accompanying the community in chanting, Pure Land practice, meditation, and Dharma sharing.
                </p>
            </article>

            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-6">
                <h2 class="mb-2">Thầy Hạnh Bảo</h2>
                <p class="mb-4 text-neutral-500">Liên Tâm Monastery, Turku – Finland</p>
                <p class="leading-8 text-neutral-700">
                    Supporting the spiritual practice of participants and helping cultivate mindfulness, stability, and harmony in the retreat setting.
                </p>
            </article>

            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-6">
                <h2 class="mb-2">Thầy Hạnh Giới</h2>
                <p class="mb-4 text-neutral-500">Viên Lạc Monastery, Varel – Germany</p>
                <p class="leading-8 text-neutral-700">
                    Co-leading the retreat, offering spiritual guidance, and helping maintain a peaceful and supportive atmosphere for the assembly.
                </p>
            </article>

            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-6">
                <h2 class="mb-2">Sangha of Affiliated Monasteries</h2>
                <p class="leading-8 text-neutral-700">
                    In addition to the main teachers, the retreat is supported by monastics from affiliated monasteries of Viên Giác Patriarchal Monastery
                    across Europe.
                </p>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
